Added linreg.c, which performs a simple linear regression.

     make linreg
     linreg -l
     etc...
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is an update which combines the ADAD and ADAF. The simple test cases implemented are the sorting of floating point arrays.

The files are:

adad.cpp        ADAD (integer) implementation
adad.h
adaf.cpp        ADAF (floating point) implentation
adaf.h
fault.cpp       fault management librart
heap.cpp        heap sort (*)
insertion.cpp   insertion sort (*)
main.cpp        main routine
Makefile        
merge.cpp       merge sort (*)
README          this file
sorter.cpp      sort routine

To compile:

copy one of the (*) files to sorter.cpp

     cp merge.cpp sorter.cpp
     make

To get the listing:

     sorter -l

To inject faults

     sorter ...
